[Course_Description]
Recruiters are an important part of your job hunting toolkit. But they need your help to get you the job you want. Help recruiters help you by learning how to partner with them on the job search. Leading recruiter and career management expert Alex Moyle shows you how to use recruiters to unlock new job opportunities and career milestones. Learn how to change the way you think about the job search, manage your expectations, and understand what to look for in a great recruiter. Using Alex’s tips, you can maximize all the potential and opportunities that recruiters offer job seekers—by working together for mutual benefit. This course was created by Careercake, the careers content platform. We are pleased to host this training in our library.